The payee tile uses the [Flexicell](/components/flexi-cell) component.

The payee tile has a few configurations, it can come with an icon to represent the payee type or the initials of the payee's name or nickname. The right side can have optional content, a date for indicating a recent payee, or an Info icon that links to more details about that payee. These configurations are most commonly used in Online Banking processes.

#### Payee with recently paid date

```tsx
<Grid>
  <GridItem span={{ initial: 12, sm: 6 }}>      
 <FlexiCell after={<FlexiCellAdornment align="center">
              <FlexiCellLabel tag="h3" rightLabel>
                Fri 5 Aug
              </FlexiCellLabel>
            </FlexiCellAdornment>} before={<FlexiCellAdornment>
              <BpayIcon color="hero" />
            </FlexiCellAdornment>} tag="a" href="#">
          <FlexiCellLabel tag="h3"> Payee name</FlexiCellLabel>
          <FlexiCellHint>Payee account details</FlexiCellHint>
        </FlexiCell>
</GridItem>
</Grid>
```

#### Payee with info icon link

```tsx
<Grid>
  <GridItem span={{ initial: 12, sm: 6 }}>           
<FlexiCell after={<FlexiCellAdornment align="center">
              <FlexiCellButton icon={() => <InfoIcon color="muted" look="outlined" />} />
            </FlexiCellAdornment>} before={<FlexiCellCircle className="bg-muted text-white" aria-label="Walter White">
              PN
            </FlexiCellCircle>} dualAction href="#">
          <FlexiCellLabel tag="h3">Payee name</FlexiCellLabel>
          <FlexiCellHint>Payee account details</FlexiCellHint>
        </FlexiCell>
</GridItem>
</Grid>
```
